{"tid":1957714,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★滙控不派息變好事---湯文亮：就當作幫了那些企業","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T08:27:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0249cc612045955be4d690b41cb69b41107ed6","tid":1957714,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不派息有助支持企業客戶</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我認為滙控不派息是為了保障客戶，在新冠疫情拖累之下，我相信不少企業是需要資金來繼續營運，不派息或多或少都可以支持那些有需要的企業，滙控支持者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>收唔到息就當作幫了那些企業</strong></span>。老實說，又不會永遠不派息，最多等兩年又會有息收。不過，對於那些等着收股息來支持日常生活費的退休人士就比較慘，現在賣又唔係，唔賣又唔係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%E6%88%96%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25A3%259E%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=419862e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%E6%88%96%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"c55d1576230977cae0769327708feded263848d5","tid":1957714,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d3b31838c62ef633328ddb23ec286